Don't know about running hotter but they are definitely heavier. I went to
Jake Raby's shop to see about a new engine and he had an aluminum case
there. He had me pick-up a mag case and then the aluminum one and it was a
lot heavier. Felt like more than 15 pounds to me.

He said he had it there to do some R&D. He still isn't using them for any of
the engines he builds.

Kevin Bell

